# Final Integration Testing

## Objective
Execute a final sweep to assure all MVP epics behave seamlessly together.

## Tasks
1. Walk through the new user registration.
2. Have a user pick up a quest, wait for peer review, and complete it.
3. Verify the correct allocation of XP, level ups, and leaderboard adjustments across multiple accounts.
4. Verify animations and UI theming present correctly.
